<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_70_r3l25"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> hans / vnd Seitʒ vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_line_1576658091944_4484">hans <expan>tuch<ex>er</ex></expan> lutʒ <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan> Jöꝛg <expan>ſtrom<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan cert="unknown">fr</expan> Pfintʒ </ab><ab facs="#facs_70_line_1576658142887_4503">ig vnd <expan>h<ex>einrich</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_70_line_1576658146721_4508"><expan>harſtörff<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r3l23"><expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab></add> Armelewte cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l29">Hawſloch / vnd cʒu <expan>gemü<ex>n</ex>de</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r3l27">geſeſʒ </ab></add> / vvie . daʒ <expan cert="unknown">h</expan> <expan>viſch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> euch cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"> hawſ </del> <expan>gemu<ex>n</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l31">
<del rend="strikethrough"> lo </del> geſeſʒen / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie </del> ein vvüre 
<del rend="strikethrough"> hoher </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r3l30"><expan>Jnne<ex>n</ex></expan> habe die ho hoher </ab></add> <expan>aufgefange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_line_1570732598336_303">ſey </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> hab </del> dann die von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l32">Rechts <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein ſülle 
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l1">damit die gemaine cʒu </ab><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l2">hawſloch vnd ʒu ge </ab><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l3"><expan>mu<ex>n</ex>de</expan> vaſt beſchedigt </ab><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l4">vverden / </ab></add> <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>Arme<ex>n</ex>man</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l33">daran vveiſen wöllet / daʒ er die 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvur </del> <expan>ſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vvüre <expan>bleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laʒ / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l34">
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del> die von rechts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein ſülle / Als vvir ew des wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_r3l35"><expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> vite Anno etc </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_70" id="33v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
