<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von Hawsen,
                                    <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, und
                                <expan>Seicze<ex>n</ex></expan> von Hawsen,
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans und Seicz, uns
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt <add>Hans
                                        <expan>Tuch<ex>er</ex></expan>. Lucz
                                        <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan>, Jörg
                                        <expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan cert="medium">Fr<ex>anz</ex></expan> Pfinczig und
                                        <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>harstörff<ex>er</ex></expan></add>,
                                <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan></add>, armelewte, czu Hawsloch und
                            czu <expan>Gemü<ex>n</ex>de</expan>
<add>gesesz</add>, wie daz <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>
<expan>Visch<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> euch czu
                                    <expan>Gemu<ex>n</ex>de</expan> geseszen, ein würe
                                        <add><expan>inne<ex>n</ex></expan> habe, die hoher</add>
<expan>aufgefange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>sey</add> dann die von rechts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                            sülle, <add>damit die gemaine czu Hawsloch und zu
                                    Ge<expan>mu<ex>n</ex>de</expan> vast beschedigt werden </add>.
                                    <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                    <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>man</expan>, daran weisen wöllet, daz er die
                                    <expan>selbe<ex>n</ex></expan> würe
                                <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laz, als die von rechts
                                    <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> sein sülle, als wir ew des wol
                                    <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Vite anno etc.</del></ab>
</div>
